<b>COMMON-----------------------------------------</b>
, ev               Open .vimrc
, ed               Open Jekyll Draft
, Space            Clear HighLight
, Shift+w          Clear WhiteSpace
q #                Macro Register on #
@ #                Call Macro on #
m #                Marking on # lines
' #                Go To Marking on #
Ctrl+y ,           Emmet
Ctrl+v             Multiline Char Select
F12                NerdTree
F11                TagBar
F10                MiniMap
Ctrl+p             FZF :Buffers
Ctrl+f             FZF :Files
gcc                Comment/Uncomment line/block
<b>SPLIT------------------------------------------</b>
(NT) i             Open File Split Horizontal
(NT) s             Open File Split Vertical
Ctrl+w s (, s)     Create Horizontal Split
Ctrl+w v (, v)     Create Vertical Split
Ctrl+w r           Switch Between 2 Split
Ctrl+w Shift+k     Move Horizontal AP to Top
Ctrl+w Shift+j     Move Horizontal AP to Bottom
Ctrl+w Shift+h     Move Vertical AP to Left
Ctrl+w Shift+l     Move Vertical AP to Right
Ctrl+w Shift++     Resize Horizontal Split Out
Ctrl+w -           Resize Horizontal Split In
Ctrl+w Shift+.     Resize Vertical Split Out
Ctrl+w Shift+,     Resize Vertical Split In
Ctrl+w Shift+-     Resize Window to Max Height
Ctrl+w Shift+&#92;     Resize Window to Max Width
Ctrl+w =           Resize Hor/Ver Equal
<b>CURSOR POSITIONING-----------------------------</b>
Shift+t            Move Cursor to Top
Shift+m            Move Cursor to Middle
Shift+l            Move Cursor to Bottom
zt                 Move Focus to Top
zz                 Move Focus to Middle
zb                 Move Focus to Bottom
<b>FOLDING----------------------------------------</b>
zf#j               Create Folds # lines
z Shift+r          Open All Folding
z Shift+m          Close All Folding
zo                 Open Selected Folding
zc                 Close Selected Folding
:mkview            Save Folding
:loadview          Load Saved Folding
